description: Gerry has summoned the doctor and finds that Ray has a head injury and may recover with rest and care. Gerry is also overcome with the sight of Ray laying so silently on the bed, but takes his lust out on the doctor, Stenley Underberger. He bends Stenley over the tub and fucks him mercilessly!
series: Triumvirate: I Saw It In Your Eyes
title: Triumvirate: I Saw It In Your Eyes, Scene #04
